  <nodes xsi:type="com.yattasolutions.diagrams:CommentVisual" xmi:id="_1vGskI7_EeyggvAY1gH3cA" sourceConnectionVisual="_1vGskY7_EeyggvAY1gH3cA" text="If the criteria is met, the balls will be set to have the same inherent traits (radius and color)&#xA;Unlike the infect strategy, the ball that passes its traits is arbitrary, so you get to see an&#xA;evolution of sorts within the population, like if smaller balls or larger balls are more likely to&#xA;pass traits based on average number of interactions.&#xA;@author charlielockyer&#xA; *" item="_1vMMII7_EeyggvAY1gH3cA">
